rebuildcloud erases the tables 'tag' and 'tag_index' and rebuilds 
their contents from the keywords associated to all the nodes, thread 
by thread.

Copy rebuildcloud.php to the root directory of your site then run the 
script:

    php -f rebuildcloud.php


